info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 30 at 9:04PM PST until February 01 at 7:00AM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM WEDNESDAY TO 7 AM PST THURSDAY... * WHAT...South winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts 35 to 45 mph with gusts up to 55 mph for higher terrain. * WHERE...Portions of southwest California. * WHEN...From 7 PM Wednesday to 7 AM PST Thursday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
